Launch GUI

Source: R/launchGUI.R
launchGUI.Rd

Launches the CATALYST Shiny app.

launchGUI()

Value

Opens a browser window with an interactive Shiny application.

Details

Detailed user guides are available inside the app. To use the app online, please visit http://imlspenticton.uzh.ch:3838/CATALYSTLite.

Examples

# NOT RUN {
launchGUI
# }
